cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.IR 

This paper discusses the application of PatternAttribution, a method for explaining deep neural network classifications, in the language domain. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). However, since the method is also applicable to other domains, it could also be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
